    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>基本示例，先上demo，一睹为快！</p>
<p>申明一个hello组件<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">var Hello = Cpage.component(&#123;</div><div class="line">    name: &apos;hello&apos;,</div><div class="line">    components: [],</div><div class="line">    template: `&lt;div&gt;&#123;&#123;hello&#125;&#125;&lt;/div&gt;`,</div><div class="line">    data: &#123;</div><div class="line">        hello: &apos;这是hello组件&apos;</div><div class="line">    &#125;,</div><div class="line">    props: &#123;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">    &#125;,</div><div class="line">    beforeRender() &#123;</div><div class="line">        console.log(&apos;beforeRender&apos;)</div><div class="line">    &#125;,</div><div class="line">    render() &#123;</div><div class="line">        console.log(&apos;render&apos;)</div><div class="line">    &#125;</div><div class="line">&#125;);</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>在根组件引用hello组件<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">var app = Cpage.component(&#123;</div><div class="line">    name: &apos;app&apos;,</div><div class="line">    components: [Hello],</div><div class="line">    template: `&lt;div&gt;&#123;&#123;text&#125;&#125;&lt;/div&gt;`,</div><div class="line">    data: &#123;</div><div class="line">        text: &apos;es5 demo&apos;</div><div class="line">    &#125;,</div><div class="line">    beforeRender() &#123;</div><div class="line">        </div><div class="line">    &#125;,</div><div class="line">    render() &#123;</div><div class="line">        </div><div class="line">    &#125;</div><div class="line">&#125;);</div><div class="line">Cpage.bootstrap(&quot;#app&quot;, app);</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
]]></content>
    
